Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海底两万哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌懦弱的人无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在作梦之前我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音乐盒开启发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:01:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#39星之继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你，对娜蒂亚开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你狠得下心\N对娜蒂亚开枪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚，快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是用你爱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚公主的意识\N已经唤不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱持着宽大的慈悲心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再给你一次活下去的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意以\N亚特兰提斯人之王的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,协助我们将愚蠢的人类\N带往正途吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案还是跟13年前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没清醒过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劝你别太小看人类，石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类并不如你所想的那么愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不认为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像那名少年\N就无法对娜蒂亚开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该毫不犹豫\N扣下扳机才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是人类的善良之处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他们的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那是不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候让你消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先让你听听\N你亲生儿子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我以友人身分送给你的\N最后一个礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼那西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃新亚特兰提斯帝国皇帝\N尼欧．伊肯．艾皮法尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石像鬼，难不成均KA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子现在不过是我的\N扯线木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼欧、娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对尼莫开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被自己的孩子杀死\N是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你将会死在自己孩子的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我这位好友的一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新鹦鹉螺号，听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新鹦鹉螺号，听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，这里是鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副船长，你平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晓得我的位置吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，追踪得到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将座标往左偏移60\N发射电子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运气好的话就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去只会坐以待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然船长就要被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成果很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们新亚特兰提斯的\N科学结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是…科学？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的肉体早在13年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被尼莫\N和巴别塔一起四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有我藉由科学的力量救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此让你的儿子多活了13年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己应该受人感谢\N而不是怨恨才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会遭到主炮直接攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的遗迹战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然刻意瞄准尼欧的控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…不可能会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼欧的意识\N明明就已经彻底消除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在竟然又恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这简直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚，快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非破坏控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则娜蒂亚不可能清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了是谁将我的身体\N改造成金属的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼那西斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼欧，你不过是个机器娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电源一断只能落得这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你连一根手指头都动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就直接下黄泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此不合乎科学的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道人的意志力\N真的足以超越科学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼那西斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我也能跟人类一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是愚蠢家伙的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闹剧就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去会直接冲入大气圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是红色诺亚\N以这样的角度根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法，只好硬干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今尼欧皇帝已经逝世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝之水的继承人就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你杀死他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他已经没有用处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就处分掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚公主\N请你将蔚蓝之水复原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并将这艘船导回正确轨道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不在乎他们的死活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身为蔚蓝之水的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定要毁灭这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要担心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新鹦鹉螺号一定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我们就一起回地球去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还是一样那么勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不知珍惜自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为凡事都能随意掌控的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是人心可不像机机一样\N能随你任意操弄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸和哥哥\N都不惜为了自己的信念牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也继承他们的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你称心如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勉强饶了她一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下你愿意让蔚蓝之水复原了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是采取合理的手段\N以求达到目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就看看心上人的尸体\N再来后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遗迹战舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强！强！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这个拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向两颗蔚蓝之水许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝之水一定会回应你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果没有蔚蓝之水\N你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不着担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是个女人\N就该优先救自己心上人的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝之水将会永远失去光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望之光…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在那道光芒中存活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有亚特兰提斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会变成盐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世上的亚特兰提斯人\N现在只剩下两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涅墨西斯．拉．阿尔果\N你是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我至今所做的一切不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟娜蒂亚两个外星人\N又能做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球已经是人类的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁将我从沉睡中唤醒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你…请你救救强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他的生命已经走到尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是尼莫船长说你可以救他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，救救强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这么一来\N你将会失去蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去你因为身为亚特兰提斯人\N而被赋予的一切力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是放弃成为神的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不需要那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你…请你救救强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这颗石头是\N亚特兰提斯人灵魂的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就将我们的生命献给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强，太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船长，尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事，全员立刻登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷稳定器受损
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎输出动力降至0.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，根本动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，没救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以说泄气话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与新鹦鹉螺号连接电源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始填充能源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离启动可能时间还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会用新鹦鹉螺号破坏发射口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为你们开出一条活路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个父亲能为你做的\N就只有这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，我也要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跟爸爸一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你体谅他的苦心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，梅蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后的事就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论遇到什么困难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都要活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在太空船里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太空船？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我们即将返回你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说错了，娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的故乡才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是你出生的星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一样都是地球人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉许了什么愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:24:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望桑森还有大家\N能早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望以后不要再发生同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.40,0:24:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（全剧终）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.65,0:24:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事到此全部结束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.09,0:24:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来向各位报告一些\N之后的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后已经过了12年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.26,0:24:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的鹦鹉螺号\N沉入了日本海沟深处
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.27,0:24:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船员们现在都过着各自的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.74,0:24:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾科哥哥和护士姊姊\N在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.54,0:25:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽朵拉则是听说\N一心一意将孩子抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.34,0:25:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强与娜蒂亚终于在5年前结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.85,0:25:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前定居勒阿弗尔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.02,0:25:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说强现在也还是一样\N和他的姑丈埋头发明
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害得娜蒂亚与姑姑\N总是有发不完的牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.83,0:25:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚虽然已经当了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.70,0:25:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却还是一样不肯吃鱼跟肉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.00,0:25:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.24,0:25:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰迪丝至今好像还是一个人\N享受着自由自在的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.11,0:25:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会永远追求\N属于自己的爱情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.32,0:25:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韩森开了间汽车公司
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.15,0:25:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了我们之中最有钱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.92,0:25:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我就只差一位漂亮老婆了”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.99,0:25:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次见面时他这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.03,0:25:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔顿听说回到英国\N乖乖继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:25:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他真的是位伯爵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.57,0:26:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑森过得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.67,0:26:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.61,0:26:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他现在是我\N玛莉．安．雷温佛洛伊的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.48,0:26:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而明年我就要跟娜蒂亚一样\N当妈妈了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.12,0:26:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的梦想就是在星期天\N全家人一起到附近的公园散步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.40,0:26:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，后会有期啰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.17,0:26:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.25,0:26:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自语仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.66,0:27:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.50,0:27:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try安慰的话语\N是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.64,0:27:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.52,0:27:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.69,0:27:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.39,0:27:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
